{"tid":718904,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：荃灣轉角見","createTime":"2018-06-27T05:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T07:36:53.000Z","uid":181719,"like":4,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c602645047245eb65806315a47ace9c23094df11","tid":718904,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"真係好轉角，要專登搵先搵到咁隱蔽嘅，但係下晝三四點（而佢冇tea set）嘅時間去，仍然要等位，可想而知生意幾好。<br />\n<br />\n叫咗個沙嗲雞扒漢堡，揭開睇沙嗲汁只有少少，但我寧願少啲，冇咁漏，雞扒煎得好香口，食落亦冇雪味，44蚊一個算幾抵食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/125852_4e0f8768eb5fa7a27e07f471146d21a7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F125852_4e0f8768eb5fa7a27e07f471146d21a7.jpeg&h=830368ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就係「型男漢堡」同佢嘅切面圖，已經盡量切靚個樣影架喇~ 唔知點解牛肉漢堡加蛋就要叫型男，可能係「牛B」咁解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 塊牛柳唔係話非常出色，但肉味同濕度合格有餘嘅，有紅菜頭夾喺中間，口感都幾新鮮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/125925_0b52be03966efbf2fd2fa74b5e3cb781.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F125925_0b52be03966efbf2fd2fa74b5e3cb781.jpeg&h=a7b21938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/125925_8a3c97eafc3e2406a43a891028db8128.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F125925_8a3c97eafc3e2406a43a891028db8128.jpeg&h=c0df6f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為食兩個包都唔覺漏，所以又嗌多咗碟炸雞翼，炸出黎稍稍燶，但都中規中矩，正常味道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/125934_77ed912bc9ad94f48b71fd25854cd95e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F125934_77ed912bc9ad94f48b71fd25854cd95e.jpeg&h=40408798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埋單好似先130蚊咁上下，真係抵食，但我敢保證同神農氏仲有幾班嘅差距。其實神農氏真係好抵屌，唔知點解連登咁多腐皮，有冇巴打可以發表下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab99c7d38c9d3830ac5232071532b232da0ec827","tid":718904,"uid":171509,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:26:08.000Z","msg":"巴打你出鱔稿做乜唔上openrice？<br />\n你係咪post錯地方？<br />\n你可唔可以發表下？"},{"pid":"e56b267e3da11b24964f7d8a68d5485e0e510281","tid":718904,"uid":3742,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌"},{"pid":"055fc48f87944941dc90120e61f2fc37c01284a0","tid":718904,"uid":24944,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"依間真係算係咁"},{"pid":"7169522d9bd92b55106e647f71a5a31f851497a8","tid":718904,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"老闆？"},{"pid":"d0cc391b0a8eda02945559a86447ca51623c5969","tid":718904,"uid":34023,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7169522d9bd92b55106e647f71a5a31f851497a8","tid":718904,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"老闆？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"f7f2fae111db528cedf218cad27ac6cf41ca2917","tid":718904,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0cc391b0a8eda02945559a86447ca51623c5969","tid":718904,"uid":34023,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7169522d9bd92b55106e647f71a5a31f851497a8","tid":718904,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"老闆？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"原來係食家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係懷疑一個人食唔食到兩個漢堡加碟雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b279c969e2e1